# S02-T05: Telegram Bot & Mini App

## Objective
Set up Telegraf bot and configure Telegram Web App integration.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `/start` command opens Mini App.
- `initData` verification on backend.
- `useTelegram.js` composable for UI interaction (back button, main button).

## Steps
1. Register bot in BotFather.
2. Implement HMAC-SHA256 verification.
3. Configure Mini App URL.
